<div class="about-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h2 class: "text-center">About Us</h2>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <!-- <img src="https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_100_100/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAsiAAAAJDhjYmZmZTdlLWRjMGEtNGIyYi04ODcwLTcyY2FiOTliNDEyMg.jpg" alt="" class="img-responsive" style="width:100%"> -->
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: "100%", alt: "Profile Image" %><br>
        <div class="about-skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="about-skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title%></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  arial-valuemax='100'
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                  >

                </div>
            </div>

          </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>



      <div class="col-md-8">

        <p>My name is Said, I'm a web and application developer based in Austin. I'm passionate about technology and the impact it has on the world. I enjoy working with others to create web applications that solve problems and improve lives. I'm enthusiastic about front-end, back-end and test driven development and functional applications. I am a Mac, *nic user. I focus on two languages: Ruby and Javascript. Ruby on Rails is my preferred framework for the development of custom rich-internet applications. Rails is ideal for new application development with fast, iterative development loops. Quickly integrate existing open-source projects and APIs to speed up development times.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target='#jobHistory'
            arial-expanded='false'
            aria-controller='jobHistory'>Job History
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target='#education'
            arial-expanded='false'
            aria-controller='education'>Education
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target='#skills'
            arial-expanded='false'
            aria-controller='skills'>Skills
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target='#passion'
            arial-expanded='false'
            aria-controller='passion'>Passion
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              This is job history
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              This is another job history
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              This is education
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              This is another education
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="skills">
            <div class="card card-block">
              This is skills
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              This is another skills
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="passion">
            <div class="card card-block">
              This is passion
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              This is another passion
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
